   472 				; SELECT = real-time record: arming clears the pattern and STARTS the clock so
   473 				; you just play in time (the live note is captured on the step under the head).
   474 				; Disarming punches out but keeps the loop playing. To step-enter instead, stop
   475 				; the clock (START) while still armed -> rec + stopped writes one step per key.
