   898 				; auto drum-machine: when DRUMBEAT>0, fire the drum every (16-DRUMBEAT) tempo
   899 				; beats (tempo beat = the sequencer step interval). Free-running (no need to
   900 				; start the sequencer); needs DRUM>0 for the hit to sound.
