  2687 				; ----- parameter descriptor tables (NPARAM entries) -------------------------
  2688 				;        0 WAVE  1 VOL  2 OCT  3 ATK  4 DEC | 5 SUS  6 REL  7 CLK  8 LFOR 9 LFOD
  2689 				;        left column (0-4)                  | right column (5-9)
  2690 				; INDEX ORDER == VISUAL ORDER so UP/DOWN steps through the panel as drawn:
  2691 				;   left column top->bottom (0-5), then right column top->bottom (6-10).
  2692 				;        0 WAVE 1 VOL 2 OCT 3 ATK 4 DEC 5 DET | 6 SUS 7 REL 8 CLK 9 LFOR 10 LFOD
  2693 				;  left column 0-5             | right column 6-11 (incl ARP=11)
  2694 				; Page 0 = indices 0-11 (osc/env/fx).  Page 2 = indices 12+ (layout positions
  2695 				; reuse the page-0 grid, so all tables index by absolute param).
